===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[ληθαργικός]]''' (''lethargikos'') "lethargic", from '''[[λήθαργος]]''' (''lethargos'') "forgetful, [[lethargy]]", from '''[[λήθη]]''' (''lethe'') "a forgetting, forgetfulness".

===Adjective===
'''lethargic'''
#[[sluggish]], [[slow]]
#[[indifferent]], [[apathetic]]

